Health facility rehabilitated:
- physical conditions of the facility prevents/limits the spread of nosocomial infections;
- the facility is safe (e.g. against natural hazards);
- WASH services available respecting standards;
- storage conditions for medical supplies are according to norms;
- medical waste is disposed of according to standards.
Use this sub-sector and indicator only if the project contributed substantially to the rehabilitation.

